        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 grid-rows-3 gap-2">
          <p class="font-ibm text-center m-0">彩 峰 黎 斗</p>
          <p class="font-ibm text-center m-0">こ ん そ め</p>
          <p class="font-ibm text-center m-0">n a g i</p>
